*Lepa* devojka je prošetala pored reke. (The beautiful girl walked by the river.)

*Lepim* pogledom me je pogledala. (She looked at me with a beautiful look.)

*Lepo* se smejala dok je pričala. (She laughed nicely while she was talking.)

*Lepša* je od sestre. (She is more beautiful than her sister.)

*Lepši* deo grada je pored plaže. (The prettier part of the city is by the beach.)

*Lepom* odećom je oduševila sve prisutne. (She delighted everyone present with her beautiful clothes.)